data.description: Welcome Home to this move in ready house on a cul-de-sac. 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Raised Ranch, 1 Car garage, with finished basement.  Hardwood floors throughout the home including under the carpet.  Fenced backyard.  You don't want to miss this diamond in the rough that has been lovingly maintained by the original owner! Convenient to Heckscher Park, the village, and harbor. Seller is Motivated!
